{"id":584380,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【立此存照】同志之声-湖南卫视芒果tv屏蔽彩虹旗/","date":"2018-05-10T07:34:12Z","modified":"2018-05-11T03:29:47Z","title":"【立此存照】同志之声 | 湖南卫视芒果TV屏蔽彩虹旗(更新)","content":"<p><strong>【更新】</strong>据@同志之声 官博透露，欧洲歌唱大赛主办方已于5月10日宣布终止中国的芒果TV的转播权。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584430\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/芒果台.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584430\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/芒果台.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"403\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/芒果台.jpg 1385w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/芒果台-300x230.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/芒果台-768x590.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/芒果台-1024x787.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1664065962/GfZXD0zqD\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@同志之声</a>：［#湖南卫视芒果TV屏蔽彩虹旗#］5月9日，@湖南卫视 旗下 @芒果TV 全网独家播出 2018 Eurovision 欧洲歌唱大赛半决赛的第一场。在芒果TV上线的视频中，爱尔兰同志选手的整段表演被直接删除，而台下粉丝挥舞的彩虹旗也被打上了马赛克，整场赛事视频中，芒果TV将所有明显可见彩虹旗的画面全部屏蔽。据悉，爱尔兰同志选手演唱参赛曲目时，伴舞的剧情是两名热恋中的男子，歌词描述的是「爱不分性别」，最后该名选手成功晋级十强，结果芒果TV独播的比赛中，却只有九强的表演。</p>\n<p>湖南卫视曾于 2000 年 12 月 20 日在当时马东主持的《有话好说》节目中推出「走近同性恋」专题，被认为是中国电视媒体首次关注同性恋。而湖南卫视也曾邀请著名同志电影《暹罗之恋》的两位主演上过《快乐大本营》。本次事件引起不少观众不满，不少网友表示这种做法是倒退。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718yuv6j21hc0u0wyo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584389\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718yuv6j21hc0u0wyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718yuv6j21hc0u0wyo.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718yuv6j21hc0u0wyo-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718t9vjj21h00rlkjl.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584388\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718t9vjj21h00rlkjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718t9vjj21h00rlkjl.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr6718t9vjj21h00rlkjl-300x156.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67b8nrtej21hc0u0u0y.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584381\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67b8nrtej21hc0u0u0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67b8nrtej21hc0u0u0y.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67b8nrtej21hc0u0u0y-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67bd7j2tj21hc0u04qr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584383\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67bd7j2tj21hc0u04qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67bd7j2tj21hc0u04qr.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67bd7j2tj21hc0u04qr-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67bcxw3lj21hc0u07wj.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584382\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/632fa1aagy1fr67bcxw3lj21hc0u07wj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net